<item>
            <title>[SOLR-359] LukeResponse.FieldInfo should expose the selected flags info and the indexInfo</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-359</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The LukeResponse has access, when reading in the NamedList to more information that is not currently being shared, like the &quot;flags&quot; for each FieldInfo and/or the indexInfo object so that more info about the fields may be used by the client.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
